OL,3,CNigel Farage: Makerfield by-election
OL,4,Cis 'biggest in half a century'
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports Political
OL,7,FCorrespondent Lise McNally spoke to
OL,8,FReform UK leader Nigel Farage about
OL,9,Fthe upcoming by-election
OL,11,FReform UK leader Nigel Farage has
OL,12,Fdubbed the upcoming Makerfield by-
OL,13,Felection "the biggest in half a
OL,14,Fcentury".
OL,16,FVoters in the Makerfield constituency
OL,17,Fwill go to the polls on 18 June, after
OL,18,FLabour MP Josh Simmons resigned to
OL,19,Fallow current Greater Manchester Mayor
OL,20,FAndy Burnham to run for Parliament.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
