OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779311467
OL,3,CNigel Farage: Makerfield by-election
OL,4,Cis 'biggest in half a century'
OL,6,FFollowing the announcement of Reform
OL,7,FUK's candidate as Robert Kenyon, Mr
OL,8,FFarage visited a pub in the
OL,9,Fconstituency.
OL,11,FHe described Andy Burnham as a "big
OL,12,Ffigure in the North West" saying "he's
OL,13,Fbeen the mayor for some time and he's
OL,14,Fbeen dubbed the King of the North".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
