OL,3,CNigel Farage: Makerfield by-election
OL,4,Cis 'biggest in half a century'
OL,6,FA statement from Wigan Council in
OL,7,FSeptember 2025 said: "The borough has
OL,8,Fapproximately 900 homes in multiple
OL,9,Foccupation - HMOs - some of which now
OL,10,Fhouse asylum seekers.
OL,12,F"Serco - the contractors who manage
OL,13,Fasylum seeker accommodation on behalf
OL,14,Fof the Government - operates around
OL,15,F300 properties in the borough for
OL,16,Fasylum seeker housing, approximately
OL,17,F200 of which are HMOs."
OL,19,FLabour currently holds a majority of
OL,20,F5,399 in Makerfield, with Reform UK in
OL,21,Fsecond, with 18% of the vote.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
