OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779311467
OL,3,CNigel Farage: Makerfield by-election
OL,4,Cis 'biggest in half a century'
OL,6,FBut in Wigan, which includes part of
OL,7,FMakerfield, Labour lost all 22 of its
OL,8,Fcouncillors in the local election,
OL,9,Fwith Reform picking up 24 of the 25
OL,10,Fseats up for grabs.
OL,12,FIn the eight Makerfield wards that
OL,13,Fvoted in the local election, Reform
OL,14,Fsecured 50% of the vote while Labour
OL,15,Fgot 23%.
OL,17,FMr Kenyon has faced claims he was
OL,18,Ffriends with fascist campaigner Gary
OL,19,FRaikes on a now deleted Facebook page,
OL,20,Fa claim that is not disputed by Reform
OL,21,FUK.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779311467
OL,3,CNigel Farage: Makerfield by-election
OL,4,Cis 'biggest in half a century'
OL,6,FIt has also been reported that Mr
OL,7,FKenyon had an X account terminated by
OL,8,FX in 2024, which Reform UK has not
OL,9,Foffered an explanation for.
OL,11,FMr Farage claimed: "there's been a lot
OL,12,Fof nonsense talked about this".
OL,14,FHe said the party cannot vet every
OL,15,Fcandidate, adding he is confident that
OL,16,FMr Kenyon, who is "a qualified
OL,17,Fplumber, ex-army reservist, family man
OL,18,Fand all round good bloke, is the right
OL,19,Fman."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
